{"tid":822162,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"明天非緊急部門公務員不用上班　學校全日停課","createTime":"2018-09-16T07:59:55.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-16T09:15:35.000Z","uid":28366,"like":2,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"9f68d12a4264d6079b0e0ef9128175d1f0c3ef78","tid":822162,"uid":28366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T07:59:55.000Z","msg":"「山竹」破壞力驚人，澳門政府公布，明日(17日)除民防架構內相關部門及駐外代表機構，政府其餘部門將關閉，並免除公務人員上班。 <br />\n<br />\n政府發言人辦公室表示，鑑於山竹對澳門造成重大影響，行政長官已作出這項批示。 <br />\n<br />\n另外，教育暨青年局宣布中、小、幼及特殊教育於明日全日停課。"},{"pid":"a56302bd8784c2929efb0c9ee48ccbe72e510794","tid":822162,"uid":65598,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T08:01:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16a2fe1b5c6b3ee7472142beaa515ffb71601de6","tid":822162,"uid":28366,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a56302bd8784c2929efb0c9ee48ccbe72e510794","tid":822162,"uid":65598,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T08:01:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T08:03:02.000Z","msg":"?"},{"pid":"f0461b3dc4a93fcd101112f1d4e1a8a4f3ac9a0a","tid":822162,"uid":45603,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T08:04:13.000Z","msg":"屌你澳門關我撚事"},{"pid":"8f03761e2785d63676443b3529522f369fa1e5d0","tid":822162,"uid":45368,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T08:04:55.000Z","msg":"香港又嬴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac2742dc2076e54774124a7d1da0ed7f78f36b1e","tid":822162,"uid":28366,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"8f03761e2785d63676443b3529522f369fa1e5d0","tid":822162,"uid":45368,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T08:04:55.000Z","msg":"香港又嬴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T08:11:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/ass